{"tid":700611,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「你沒有好結果」原唱版本真係聽到毛骨悚然","createTime":"2018-06-13T12:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T11:21:19.000Z","uid":71166,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"97d0d2eebb9e7c5684dec035f6e694ef74dc67ad","tid":700611,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"原唱：李蕙敏<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/I2X5oZRhiSc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FI2X5oZRhiSc&d=E53vm%2Fe9zDsGBEJNBXY9RMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=61cebac9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/I2X5oZRhiSc</a><br />\n<br />\n係一種愛中帶恨，被心愛男人浪費青春，丟棄，玩弄，欺壓，反悔而帶嚟嘅恨，完完全全想毀滅個男人，聽過幾個cover都聽唔到嗰個恨同絕望帶又帶點不捨嘅感覺，Amanda 真係好得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，加埋黃偉文句句入心入肺歌詞，有種心寒感覺&hellip;&hellip;好想比Amanda 喺耳邊同我講「你沒有好結果」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e20ed546915c44588a9c0b3d4ae1ef77cf88b2","tid":700611,"uid":71166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:56:32.000Z","msg":"李蕙敏 <br />\n<br />\n你沒有好結果<br />\n<br />\n作詞：黃偉文<br />\n作曲：葉健華/麥皓輪<br />\n編曲：麥皓輪<br />\n<br />\n傷了的女人別走這樣近<br />\n被人拋棄的女人殘忍<br />\n全都怪你離開我　臨走也繼續傷我<br />\n見我粉身碎骨還點上一把火<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可以死了心但忍不住恨<br />\n但求天會追究這男人<br />\n仍相信有場好戲　命中已註定等你<br />\n報應日漸臨近來清算你罪行</span><br />\n<br />\n＊今天淌血是我心<br />\n　即將痛在你心　身份對調發生<br />\n　<span style=\"color: red;\">來讓你一生最喜歡和珍惜那人<br />\n　也摧毀你一生完全沒半點惻隱</span><br />\n<br />\n    等欣賞你被某君<br />\n　一刀插入你心　加點眼淚陪襯<br />\n　來讓你清楚我當初嘗到的折磨<br />\n　你親身試清楚如凡事亦有因果＊<br />\n<br />\n這算不算狠我撫心自問<br />\n沒人想變得那麼殘忍<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果見你離開我　日子更快樂的過<br />\n我會傷得更深餘生也不甘心</span><br />\n<br />\nREPEAT＊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n將當天那自卑感當天那無依感<br />\n都雙倍回贈你<br />\n來讓你清楚我當初嘗到的折磨<br />\n也親身試清楚如凡事亦有因果</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f072b6d59f434e19118a2cfebd4f03d06864d07e","tid":700611,"uid":56716,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:58:37.000Z","msg":"終極怨婦歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲怨過破相多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99128f5829c4c9af9c16cda31cf242f9857f92ab","tid":700611,"uid":71166,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:00:13.000Z","msg":"再聽下呢個yy演唱會版本<br />\n好聽到似一個經歷 <br />\n可以感受一個女人嘅不甘<br />\n賠上歲有，青春，過去現在將來，一無所有。。。<br />\n弘聽到哭了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8pblaYklSbs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8pblaYklSbs&d=E53vm%2Fe9zDsGBEJNBXY9RMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6da98c39\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8pblaYklSbs</a>"},{"pid":"401ad05425eebcdd29239b53785f5e63db789ebb","tid":700611,"uid":120418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c69cf2fc92a1ae0502ef171255236d8e64e422b","tid":700611,"uid":71004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quot